How to install Go Lang:

Step 1: Open golang.org/dl/
        Download Lastest Version Of Go Linux.

Step 2: Open Terminal 
        tar -xvf go tab -C /usr/local
        
Step 3: Change Permission:
        chown -R root:root /usr/local/go/
        gedit ~/.profile
        
        Notepade will Open and paste this line after True
       
        export PATH=$PATH:$GOPATH/bin
        export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin
        
        Save
        
        type in terminal: . ~/.profile
        
        go version
        
 Finish:
